snippet: Mark Webber beat Red Bull teammate Sebastian Vettel’s time at the end of qualifying Saturday to take the pole position for the Abu Dhabi Grand Prix in United Arab Emirates.
lead_paragraph: Mark Webber beat Red Bull teammate Sebastian Vettel’s time at the end of qualifying Saturday to take the pole position for the Abu Dhabi Grand Prix in United Arab Emirates.

headline.main: Webber Grabs Pole in Abu Dhabi Grand Prix
headline.print_headline: Webber Grabs Pole in Abu Dhabi
